        "recommendation": "REJECT completely. This is a deal-breaker. NEGOTIATE: We retain all ownership of our platform and existing IP. Customer receives limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable license for term of agreement. We own any enhancements to core platform. Customer owns only customer-specific custom integrations (if any).",
        "business_impact": "Existential threat to business - we would lose ownership of our product"
      }
    ]
